923
01:01:54,960 --> 01:01:58,590
很抱歉，我不同意你在诺斯伍德的律师的分析
So, I'm sorry, I disagree with the assessment of your lawyer at Northwood.

924
01:01:58,670 --> 01:01:59,670
同意
Agreed.

925
01:02:01,130 --> 01:02:04,550
希望“她是个贴心的小女孩”这评价没有包含你的判断
I hope the fact that she's a sweet little girl is not clouding your judgment.

926
01:02:04,630 --> 01:02:07,010
如果这些人离开
Dozens of other little girls' lives

927
01:02:07,090 --> 01:02:09,850
几十个其他小女孩的生命就会有危险
are at stake if these men leave.

928
01:02:09,970 --> 01:02:12,390
对不起，但白宫的吉丽安·古德曼小姐
I'm sorry, but we have a Miss Jillian Goldman from the White House

929
01:02:12,470 --> 01:02:13,770
要求接入通话
asking to be patched in.

930
01:02:13,850 --> 01:02:15,350
- 谁？  - 吉丽安·古德曼
Who? Jillian Goldman.

931
01:02:15,440 --> 01:02:18,810
她是美国国家安全委员会的高级法律顾问
She's a Senior Legal Adviser at the US National Security Council.

932
01:02:18,900 --> 01:02:20,770
国务卿把情况向她简要介绍了
She's been briefed by the Secretary of State.

933
01:02:20,860 --> 01:02:22,280
接过来
Put her through.

934
01:02:25,490 --> 01:02:28,070
下午好，谢谢你们允许我评论
Good afternoon and thank you for allowing me to comment.

935
01:02:28,160 --> 01:02:29,740
是的，谢谢你加入我们
Yeah, thanks for joining us.

936
01:02:29,830 --> 01:02:31,910
你们也知道作为军队成员
As the military members of your committee know,

937
01:02:31,990 --> 01:02:35,250
我们有个与附带损失评估相关的评分系统
we have a point system that takes into account collateral damage

938
01:02:35,330 --> 01:02:38,460
来推断一个行动究竟是否合法
to deduce what is and what is not a legal strike.

939
01:02:38,540 --> 01:02:40,630
我直接跟你说吧
And let me tell you categorically

940
01:02:40,750 --> 01:02:42,760
这新情况的存在
that the existence of this new circumstance

941
01:02:42,840 --> 01:02:45,550
不会让我们超出合法军事行动的范畴
does not push us beyond a legitimate military action.

942
01:02:45,630 --> 01:02:48,800
我们的这一行动远远称不上“有争议”
We are way off what we would consider a dispute in this matter.

943
01:02:48,890 --> 01:02:52,220
古德曼小姐，我们对附带损伤这个问题
Miss Goldman, we have a somewhat different approach

944
01:02:52,310 --> 01:02:53,930
有不同的看法
to the question of collateral damage.

945
01:02:54,020 --> 01:02:55,930
先生，你必须现在行动，你有两个人
Sir, you must act now. You have two men

946
01:02:56,020 --> 01:02:58,060
即将开始自杀式任务
about to embark on a suicide mission.

947
01:02:58,150 --> 01:02:59,940
你已经监控了总统东非清除名单上的
You have number two, four, and five

948
01:03:00,020 --> 01:03:02,780
第二、四和五号人物
on the President's East Africa kill list in your sights,

949
01:03:02,860 --> 01:03:04,440
你要因为一个附带损失
and you are putting the whole mission at risk

950
01:03:04,530 --> 01:03:06,990
就让整个任务遇到危机？
because of one collateral damage issue?

951
01:03:07,070 --> 01:03:09,450
我意识到这次任务是你发起的
I realize that this mission is your call,

952
01:03:09,530 --> 01:03:11,120
如果你让这些人去
but there would be some mighty angry people

953
01:03:11,200 --> 01:03:14,370
把一个购物中心炸上天，那你将面对…
here at the White House and at the Pentagon, and out there in the world

954
01:03:14,830 --> 01:03:16,210
来自白宫，五角大楼
if you allow these people to leave

955
01:03:16,330 --> 01:03:17,660
以及世界各地的人民的愤怒
and blow a shopping mall to kingdom come.

956
01:03:17,750 --> 01:03:20,130
对不起，外交部长想加入
I'm sorry. We have the Foreign Secretary wanting to join.

957
01:03:20,210 --> 01:03:22,590
好的，感谢你的意见，古德曼小姐
Right. We appreciate your thoughts, Miss Goldman.

958
01:03:22,670 --> 01:03:23,670
谢谢
Thank you.

959
01:03:23,800 --> 01:03:24,800
谢谢你
Thank you.

960
01:03:26,220 --> 01:03:28,720
大家下午好，请原谅我这身衣服
Good afternoon, everybody. Excuse my appearance.

961
01:03:28,800 --> 01:03:30,890
这边是晚上，我还有点水土不服
It's night here, and I have a bout of food poisoning.

962
01:03:30,970 --> 01:03:32,930
抱歉把你从病床上拉起来
Sorry to drag you from your sick bed.

963
01:03:33,010 --> 01:03:34,470
没错
That's quite all right.

964
01:03:34,970 --> 01:03:37,310
乔治，我理解的是对的吗
George, do I understand this correctly?

965
01:03:37,390 --> 01:03:39,440
关于等待那女孩
There's a legal argument for waiting

966
01:03:39,520 --> 01:03:41,770
给她个机会把饼卖完，还存在法律上的争论？
and giving this girl a chance to sell her bread?

967
01:03:42,060 --> 01:03:43,110
是的
Yes, there is.

968
01:03:43,190 --> 01:03:44,780
但相反的，这不意味着
But, conversely, it does not mean

969
01:03:44,860 --> 01:03:46,650
现在发射武器
that there is not also a legal argument

970
01:03:46,740 --> 01:03:48,530
就不会带来法律问题
for releasing the weapon now.

971
01:03:49,570 --> 01:03:50,990
请原谅，我不知道这对我有什么帮助
Forgive me, I'm not sure that helps me.

972
01:03:51,070 --> 01:03:54,830
外交部长，现在采取军事行动是必须的
Foreign Secretary, there is a military necessity for acting now.

973
01:03:54,910 --> 01:03:59,330
在我们看来，他们随时会离开那幢房子
In our view, they'll be making a move from that house at any moment.

974
01:03:59,410 --> 01:04:04,040
先生们，有什么任务是合法的推荐给我的？
Gentlemen, what action is being legally recommended to me?

975
01:04:04,130 --> 01:04:07,050
詹姆斯，法律争论是我们可以等
James, the legal argument is that we could wait,

976
01:04:07,130 --> 01:04:08,840
但不需要等的
but we need not wait.

977
01:04:08,920 --> 01:04:12,010
军事行动方面的争议则是不能等
And the military argument is that we should not wait.

978
01:04:12,090 --> 01:04:13,430
- 对吗  - 没错
Right? Exactly.

979
01:04:18,980 --> 01:04:22,310
是我建议不应该拖延
It's my recommendation that we should not delay

980
01:04:22,440 --> 01:04:24,360
执行这次任务
in proceeding with this mission.

981
01:04:24,440 --> 01:04:26,230
如果现在不行动，就会冒着
If we don't act now, we risk losing

982
01:04:26,320 --> 01:04:27,820
失去八十条人命的风险
the lives of up to 80 people.

983
01:04:27,900 --> 01:04:30,030
这些死亡你只能估算
You can only assume those deaths.

984
01:04:30,110 --> 01:04:32,530
能确定的是，如果我们现在行动
What is certain is that if we do act now,

985
01:04:32,610 --> 01:04:34,320
这一个女孩会很惨
this one girl will suffer.

986
01:04:35,410 --> 01:04:38,580
你会救她，然后搭上另外八十条性命？
And you would save her and risk killing 80 others?

987
01:04:42,120 --> 01:04:45,710
对，我会救她然后冒那个险
Yes, I would save her and take that risk.

988
01:04:45,790 --> 01:04:47,460
那就是我会做的
That is what I would do.

989
01:04:47,800 --> 01:04:51,720
安吉拉，到时候电视报道
Angela, is it you or me who will be invited onto the Today program

990
01:04:51,800 --> 01:04:53,430
商场炸弹袭击中八十人丧生
to explain why we knew of the attack

991
01:04:53,550 --> 01:04:55,140
而我们却没有阻止
on a shopping center that killed 80 people,

992
01:04:55,220 --> 01:04:57,100
他们会请的人是你还是我？
but chose to do nothing to stop it?

993
01:04:59,100 --> 01:05:00,270
是你，詹姆斯
You, James.

994
01:05:01,100 --> 01:05:04,940
但说实话，从政治上说，我更愿意指出
But frankly, politically, I'd rather point to Al-Shabab

995
01:05:05,020 --> 01:05:06,730
青年党才是杀死八十人的凶手
as murderers of 80 people shopping

996
01:05:06,820 --> 01:05:08,570
而不是为我们的军队发起的
than have to defend a drone attack

997
01:05:08,650 --> 01:05:11,530
害死一名无辜女孩的无人机攻击辩护
by our forces that kills an innocent child.

998
01:05:19,450 --> 01:05:22,540
詹姆斯，安吉拉这个观点很明确
James, Angela makes a compelling point.

999
01:05:23,750 --> 01:05:28,250
如果青年党杀死八十个人，我们就能赢得道义
If Al-Shabab kill 80 people, we win the propaganda war.

1000
01:05:29,050 --> 01:05:32,170
如果我们杀一个孩子，他们就赢
If we kill one child, they do.

1001
01:05:35,680 --> 01:05:37,100
那我们什么都不做？
So, we don't do it?

1002
01:05:38,350 --> 01:05:39,850
她有个客人
She's got a customer.

1003
01:06:15,510 --> 01:06:18,010
我建议你盯着另一个屏幕
I suggest you keep your eyes on the other screen.

1004
01:06:19,600 --> 01:06:21,140
恕我直言，外交部长
With respect, Foreign Secretary,

1005
01:06:21,220 --> 01:06:23,890
另外八十条人命也包括无辜的孩子
are the lives of 80 people, including innocent children,

1006
01:06:23,980 --> 01:06:27,020
为了赢得道义真的需要付出这么大的代价吗
really worth the price of winning the propaganda war?

1007
01:06:29,110 --> 01:06:32,190
将军，如果我们攻击，我们攻击的视频会泄露吗
General, if we go ahead, might footage of our attack be leaked?

1008
01:06:32,280 --> 01:06:34,950
长官，来自掠食者的视频是绝对安全的
Sir, the footage from the Reaper is completely secure.

1009
01:06:35,030 --> 01:06:36,820
将军，如果我们不再等一会
General, I would feel uncomfortable

1010
01:06:36,910 --> 01:06:39,530
我会觉得不安的
if we did not at least wait a little longer.

1011
01:06:40,030 --> 01:06:44,710
如果我们攻击，视频泄露这女孩被杀
If we go ahead and footage is leaked and this girl is killed,

1012
01:06:44,790 --> 01:06:47,210
我认为国内民众会非常反感
then, I think, the country would be most disturbed.

1013
01:06:47,290 --> 01:06:49,000
外交部长，我们的任务就是
Foreign Secretary, it is our task

1014
01:06:49,130 --> 01:06:50,840
做出正确的军事决定
to make the right military decision.

1015
01:06:50,920 --> 01:06:52,500
我们不能参与到将来视频网站上
We cannot engage in an argument

1016
01:06:52,590 --> 01:06:54,920
可能发生的争论之中
about possible future postings on YouTube.

1017
01:06:55,010 --> 01:06:58,930
恕我直言，将军，那些网站上的视频连革命都能煽动
With respect, General, revolutions are fueled by postings on YouTube.

1018
01:07:18,610 --> 01:07:20,370
我认为既然后果会这么严重
I think the consequences are such

1019
01:07:20,490 --> 01:07:22,280
我们需要获得首相的许可
that we need clearance from the PM.

1020
01:07:22,370 --> 01:07:26,540
詹姆斯，你有作出决定的权力
James! You have the authority to make a decision!

1021
01:07:26,620 --> 01:07:28,460
不，我告诉你，你得把问题教给他
No, I'm telling you. You need to take it to him.

1022
01:07:29,790 --> 01:07:32,250
先生，首相今天下午要在斯特拉斯堡发表演讲
Sir, the PM is giving a speech in Strasbourg this afternoon,

1023
01:07:32,340 --> 01:07:34,340
可能不太好打断
and may not be easily interrupted.

1024
01:07:34,420 --> 01:07:36,090
这就交给你解决了，杰克
I'll leave you to sort that one out, Jack.

1025
01:07:36,550 --> 01:07:37,550
是，先生
Yes, sir.

1026
01:07:38,970 --> 01:07:40,550
我去联系他
I'll track him down.

1027
01:08:30,350 --> 01:08:31,690
喂
Yes?

1028
01:08:31,770 --> 01:08:33,650
长官，怎么了
Ma'am, what's happening?

1029
01:08:33,730 --> 01:08:35,650
你在待命中，中尉
You're on standby, Lieutenant.

1030
01:08:36,480 --> 01:08:37,690
是
Yes, ma'am.

1031
01:08:42,240 --> 01:08:44,240
还在踢皮球
Still on the chain.

1032
01:09:00,760 --> 01:09:01,760
还剩两块面饼
Two loaves left.

1033
01:09:01,840 --> 01:09:03,220
我们得等等
We gotta wait now.

1034
01:09:08,930 --> 01:09:10,100
快啊
Come on.

1035
01:10:38,360 --> 01:10:39,400
长官，电池没电了
Ma'am, the battery died.

1036
01:10:39,480 --> 01:10:41,480
我们的人倒下了，我们没法替换
Our man is down. We can't replace it.

1037
01:10:41,980 --> 01:10:43,070
天啊
Christ.

1038
01:10:48,370 --> 01:10:50,120
- 出什么事了  - 电池
What happened? Battery.

1039
01:10:50,200 --> 01:10:51,530
噢，天啊
Oh, for God's sake!

1040
01:10:52,290 --> 01:10:54,500
现在我们不知道他们在干什么了
Now we have no idea what they're doing.

1041
01:10:55,500 --> 01:10:56,580
我也许有个办法
I might have a solution.

1042
01:10:57,210 --> 01:10:58,830
如果我的瞄准手能够计算出
If my targeteer can calculate us

1043
01:10:58,920 --> 01:11:02,090
女孩遭遇附带损伤的几率在百分之五十以下
coming in under 50% for collateral damage on the girl,

1044
01:11:02,170 --> 01:11:03,670
你那边能够获得许可吗
do you think you can get approval at your end?

1045
01:11:07,180 --> 01:11:08,340
是的
Yes, I do.

1046
01:11:08,930 --> 01:11:10,260
谢谢
Thanks.

1047
01:11:15,850 --> 01:11:17,020
电池
Battery.

1048
01:11:21,520 --> 01:11:22,570
赛德中士
Sergeant Saddiq,

1049
01:11:23,190 --> 01:11:25,610
我们想把这边这条街的附带损伤
we're looking to present the collateral damage

1050
01:11:25,690 --> 01:11:30,410
算出致命度在百分之四十到百分之五十之间
in the street, in this area right here, as 45 to 50% fatality.

1051
01:11:30,490 --> 01:11:32,280
你认为那可能吗
Do you think that's possible?

1052
01:11:32,370 --> 01:11:35,160
我算出来的是六十五到七十五
I've calculated a 65 to 75.

1053
01:11:35,250 --> 01:11:36,620
是的，当然
Yes, yes. Sure, sure,

1054
01:11:36,710 --> 01:11:39,000
但你知道，如果我们把导弹瞄准这里和这里
but, you know, if we put the payload here, or here,

1055
01:11:39,540 --> 01:11:41,540
或者也许这里
or maybe here,

1056
01:11:41,630 --> 01:11:43,710
那就能确保目标致命
well, then we could guarantee the target fatality,

1057
01:11:43,800 --> 01:11:45,880
但能降低损伤
but we could reduce the collateral.

1058
01:11:47,590 --> 01:11:50,890
或者也许能让导弹瞄准这里
Or maybe we could target the missile right here, look.

1059
01:11:51,590 --> 01:11:52,800
是，长官
Yes, ma'am.

1060
01:11:53,720 --> 01:11:55,220
你能不能…
Will you just...

1061
01:11:56,560 --> 01:12:00,190
尽你一切所能救这女孩的命
You just do whatever you can to save this girl's life.

1062
01:12:00,270 --> 01:12:01,770
我就交给你了
I'll leave it with you.

1063
01:12:03,270 --> 01:12:04,610
是
Yes, ma'am.

1064
01:12:10,570 --> 01:12:12,320
如果我们要向内罗毕的人宣布
If we have to announce to the people of Nairobi

1065
01:12:12,410 --> 01:12:13,990
我们知道一切但没有行动…
that we knew everything but did nothing...

1066
01:12:14,080 --> 01:12:16,750
我们不需要宣布我们知道任何事，将军
We do not have to announce that we knew anything, General.

1067
01:12:19,120 --> 01:12:23,290
首相要我们尽可能减小伤亡
The PM asks that we do what we can to minimize casualties.

1068
01:12:23,420 --> 01:12:25,090
- 该死的懦夫  - 你以为我们在干什么
Bloody coward! What do you think we're doing?

1069
01:12:25,170 --> 01:12:26,250
你怎么理解这话，乔治
How do you interpret that, George?

1070
01:12:26,340 --> 01:12:28,260
部长，我们不能让受命于政府的委员会
Minister, we cannot have military decisions

1071
01:12:28,420 --> 01:12:30,300
来做出军事方面的决定
dictated by government committees.

1072
01:12:30,430 --> 01:12:33,350
更不能在军事行动的每个阶段都停下来
Nor can we put on hold a military operation at every stage

1073
01:12:33,430 --> 01:12:35,140
等待法律许可
for legal clarification.

1074
01:12:35,220 --> 01:12:37,600
你让我们什么时候去打仗，我们就打
You tell us when to go to war, we conduct the war,

1075
01:12:37,680 --> 01:12:38,850
剩下的你来处理
you deal with the aftermath.

1076
01:12:38,930 --> 01:12:40,940
要那么简单就好了
If only it were that simple.

1077
01:12:55,370 --> 01:12:57,660
抱歉又要催你了，中士，但我们没多少时间
Sorry to rush you, Sergeant, but we don't have much time.

1078
01:12:57,740 --> 01:12:59,120
是
Yes, ma'am.

1079
01:13:04,630 --> 01:13:05,790
长官
Ma'am.

1080
01:13:07,340 --> 01:13:10,050
- 把攻击点调到这里  - 嗯哼
Adjusting the point of impact to here... Mmm-hmm.

1081
01:13:10,170 --> 01:13:12,880
致命几率就只有百分之四十五到百分之六十五
There is a 45 to 65% possibility of fatality.

1082
01:13:12,970 --> 01:13:14,590
- 百分之六十五  - 对
65%? Yes.

1083
01:13:14,680 --> 01:13:18,390
不，我需要把计算结果降到百分之五十以下
No, I need that calculation to be below 50%.

1084
01:13:20,890 --> 01:13:23,190
也许能评估一下
Perhaps there could be an assessment

1085
01:13:23,310 --> 01:13:25,560
目标点在这里的损伤
of the impact of the damage right here.

1086
01:13:25,650 --> 01:13:29,360
计算结果已经是我认为最低的了
That calculation is already at the lowest limit of what I believe is possible.

1087
01:13:31,360 --> 01:13:33,530
要是让导弹击中这里呢
What if you put the missile there?

1088
01:13:33,610 --> 01:13:34,570
我还是必须
I would still have to make that

1089
01:13:34,660 --> 01:13:37,160
把可能上限定为百分之六十五
a 65% possibility on the upper limit.

1090
01:13:40,080 --> 01:13:42,000
中士，我们要让行动成功
Sergeant, we need to make this work.

1091
01:13:44,830 --> 01:13:46,330
你明白吗
Do you understand?

1092
01:13:47,840 --> 01:13:49,880
我们已经锁定了目标
We are locked into this kill chain.

1093
01:13:49,960 --> 01:13:52,380
我们必须作出决定，有…
